NK090(u)006:1: // spyi mdo dgongs 'dus kyi 'chad thabs zin bris nyung ngu rnam gsal bzhugs so //
NK090(u)006:2: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi ngang //
NK090(u)006:4: thams cad rig pa phyag rgya'i sku //
NK090(u)006:5: bla ma rdo rje rgyal por 'dud //
NK090(u)006:6: rnal 'byor bzhi bcu'i nyi ma yi //
NK090(u)006:7: 'od zer d+r+wa ba chen po'i bdag /dpal ldan rgyud kyi rgyal po yi //
NK090(u)006:9: de la lung chen a nu yo ga'i spyi mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa'i rgyud 'chad pa la /
NK090(u)006:10: slob ma mdo rang lugs kyi phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang gis smin pa rnams la /
NK090(u)006:11: gnas dus phun sum tshogs par rtsa ba gsum gyi
NK090(u)006:12: rten bkram pa'i spyan sngar stegs bu la ras bris
NK090(u)006:13: kyi dkyil 'khor bkram phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod tshogs
NK090(u)006:14: bshams nas / mdo rang lugs sgrub dbang grags pa'i
NK090(u)006:15: chu bo dang 'brel ba'i dur khrod gsang mchog gi
NK090(u)006:16: bshams nas / rtsa dkyil lam / phyi dkyil tshogs
NK090(u)006:17: chen 'dus pa gter chen bla mas mdzad pa ltar
NK090(u)006:18: bzlas pa grub kyi bar bya /
NK090(u)006:22: lung chen a nu yo ga'i rgyud thams cad kyi
NK090(u)006:23: rgyal po sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i
NK090(u)006:24: mdo chen po'i bshad bka' zab mo zhu ba'i yon
NK090(u)006:25: du dmigs nas man+dala 'bul bar zhu /
NK090(u)006:26: zhes brda sprad la tshom bu so bdun ma rgyas par phul mthar /
NK090(u)006:28: so so rang rang gi dbu gtsug tu pam las
NK090(u)006:29: pad+ma dang a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng
NK090(u)006:30: du bla ma dang gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje
NK090(u)006:31: sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK090(u)006:32: rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin cing /
NK090(u)006:33: de'i pang du yum snyems ma dkar mo gri gug
NK090(u)006:34: dang thod pa 'dzin pas 'khyud cing mnyam par sbyor
NK090(u)006:35: ba'i yab kyi thugs kar zla ba'i steng du h'u
NK090(u)006:36: dkar po'i mthar sngags phreng kha dog dkar po g.yas
NK090(u)006:38: yi ge brgya pa gsol 'debs kyi tshul du bzlas
NK090(u)006:39: pas sku dang sngags phreng las bdud rtsi'i rgyun dpag
NK090(u)006:42: lus kyi nang thams cad gang /
NK090(u)006:43: nad gdon sdig ltung thams cad lhag med du byang
NK090(u)006:44: bar mos la yi ge brgya pa lhan cig tu
NK090(u)006:45: bzla bar zhu / zhes yi ge brgya pa lan nyer gcig tsam bzla /
NK090(u)006:46: mgon po bdag ni mi shes sogs dang /
NK090(u)006:48: mdzad du gsol bar dpon slob lhan du 'don /
NK090(u)006:49: zhes gsol ba btab pas sdig sgrib dag pa'i gnang
NK090(u)006:50: ba byin nas rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum so
NK090(u)006:51: so rang rang la thim par gyur /
NK090(u)006:52: nyin gnyis pa man 'chad dbang nyan dbang la 'jug /slob dpon gyis /
NK090(u)006:53: cho 'phrul 'byung ba'i glu 'dis gsol ba btab pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK090(u)006:54: ye shes sgyu ma'i rnam par rol pa'i sku //
NK090(u)006:55: thabs dang shes rab che la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK090(u)006:56: 'phags rje sprul pa mang po 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK090(u)006:57: bder gshegs bde bar gshegs pa bzhes su gsol /
NK090(u)006:59: slar yang rdo rje rol pa de kho na'i glus bskul te gsol ba btab pa 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK090(u)006:61: yid bzhin sku mchog nam mkha' lta bu la //
NK090(u)006:62: khyab pa'i byin rlabs rdo rje gar mdzad cing //
NK090(u)006:63: gzi brjid sprin phung rol bas bsgyings pa'i sku //
NK090(u)006:64: thogs med rdo rje rol pa'i cho 'phrul ston //
NK090(u)006:66: yid bzhin gsung mchog sgra brnyan lta bu las //
NK090(u)006:67: snyan pa'i byin rlabs rdo rje brjod mdzad cing //
NK090(u)006:68: yan lag rgya mtsho mi zad bkod pa'i gsung //
NK090(u)006:69: seng ge'i sgra yis gsang sngags rgya mtsho ston //
NK090(u)006:71: ye shes snying po nyi ma lta bu las //
NK090(u)006:72: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rdo rje bde mdzad cing //
NK090(u)006:73: thig le spros bral rnam par mi rtog thugs //
NK090(u)006:74: rnam grol de nyid nges pa'i cho 'phrul ston //
NK090(u)006:75: mi shes blun rmongs 'dam bying 'gro ba rnams //
NK090(u)006:76: sdug bsngal d+r+wa bas bcings pa thabs kyis dgrol //
NK090(u)006:77: ma rig mun pas long ba don gyis phye //
NK090(u)006:78: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho rol pa'i glu yis sgrol //
NK090(u)006:79: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi thugs chen po //
NK090(u)006:80: ye shes don gyi snying po mchog dang ldan //
NK090(u)006:81: rnal 'byor theg chen rdo rje kun 'dus lung //
NK090(u)006:82: 'dus pa'i tshogs la rgya cher bshad du gsol //
NK090(u)006:83: a hoh lan gcig /de nas gsang sgo dbye bar gsol ba btab pa 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK090(u)006:84: gsang ba chen po'i rigs tshogs su //
NK090(u)006:85: de nas bdag ni 'jug par bya //
NK090(u)006:86: phyir mi ldog par lung thob phyir //
NK090(u)006:87: bdag la gsang sgo dbye bar gasalo //
NK090(u)006:89: nyin gnyis pa man 'di nas 'jug /bla ma dang
NK090(u)006:90: gnyis su med pa'i dpal chen po yab yum mnyam
NK090(u)006:91: par sbyor ba'i mkha' gsang las nyi zla byang chub
NK090(u)006:92: sems kyi 'od zer gyi sprin 'phros pas rgyud nyan
NK090(u)006:93: pa la mi dbang ba'i dri ma thams cad phral
NK090(u)006:94: te don la nges par 'jug pa'i gsang sgo phye
NK090(u)006:95: bar gyur / slob dpon rang nyid lce la smra
NK090(u)006:96: byed kyi thig le nyid h+r+aihyiga gzung las snang ba
NK090(u)006:97: mtha' yas yab yum dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu
NK090(u)006:99: gnas gsum las 'phros pa'i 'od kyis de bzhin gshegs
NK090(u)006:100: pa tha mas cad kyi gsung rdo rje 'od kyi
NK090(u)006:101: rnam par bsdus te thim pas chos 'chad pa la
NK090(u)006:102: sgrib pa'i dri ma thams cad dag /slob dpon rang
NK090(u)006:103: nyid lha dang bcas pa 'od du zhu ba las
NK090(u)006:104: snang ba mtha' yas kyi skur gyur /
NK090(u)006:106: slob bu'i rna ba gnyis su bdud rtsi'i thig le bya /
NK090(u)006:107: nyin gnyis pa phan chad thig le mi dgos /
NK090(u)006:108: slob bu'i rna ba gnyis su nyan shes kyi thig
NK090(u)006:109: le nyid t+r+aamhyiga zung las rin chen 'byung ldan yab
NK090(u)006:110: yum ser po rin chen dang dril bu 'dzin pa'i
NK090(u)006:111: skur gyur / gnas gsum las 'phros pa'i 'od zer
NK090(u)006:112: gyis tshig dang don gyi gzungs la sogs pa de
NK090(u)006:113: bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan rin po che'i gter thams
NK090(u)006:114: cad 'od kyi rnam par bsdus nas thim pas /
NK090(u)006:115: chos nyan pa la sgrib pa'i dri ma thams cad
NK090(u)006:116: dag /slob ma lha dang bcas pa 'od du zhu
NK090(u)006:117: ba las rin chen 'byung ldan gyi skur gyur /
NK090(u)006:118: nyin gnyis pa man bdud tshar gcod kyi sngags la 'jug /nyin dang po la /
NK090(u)006:119: t+r+aam las byung ba'i rin 'byung gi ngo bo rgyud kyi glegs bam gtad de /
NK090(u)006:120: t+r+aamh gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog rnam gsum gyi //
NK090(u)006:121: gsang ba'i don la nyan cing slob pa'i dbang //
NK090(u)006:122: dbang thob skal ldan khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK090(u)006:123: bdud rtsi'i chu 'dis gsang ba'i gsang sgo dbye //
NK090(u)006:124: sarba ta th+aa ga ta d+harma sid+d+hi hoh na mo /
NK090(u)006:125: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK090(u)006:126: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la nyan pa'i
NK090(u)006:127: dbang bskur bas gsang ba'i bka' mtha' dag nyan pa'i
NK090(u)006:128: dbang dam pa mtha' dag thob par gyur cig /bla
NK090(u)006:129: ma dpal chen pos 'khor rnam par sbyang ba'i ched
NK090(u)006:130: du shangs kyi h'u ring las byang chub kyi sems
NK090(u)006:131: sprin las khro bo'i tshogs dpag tu med pa spros
NK090(u)006:132: pas bgegs dang log par 'dren pa'i tshogs thams cad
NK090(u)006:133: rgyang ring du bskrad par gyur /
NK090(u)006:136: theg chen dam pa'i rigs can rnams //
NK090(u)006:137: bla 'og rim pa ji bzhin du //
NK090(u)006:138: rdo rje gsang ba'i gral bkod de //
NK090(u)006:139: rigs ma yin pa rigs med 'gyur //
NK090(u)006:140: rigs can rnams kyi dam tshig ni //
NK090(u)006:142: de las 'das na de brlag byed //
NK090(u)006:143: h'u kro d+ha dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK090(u)006:144: rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK090(u)006:147: khyed rang rnams kyis rmad du byung ba'i me tog dang /
NK090(u)006:148: ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa sna tshogs pa 'bul ba'i mos pa dang bcas te 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK090(u)006:149: rdo rje rgyal po tshogs bdag dgongs su gsol //
NK090(u)006:150: chos kyi rgyal po mi g.yo rgyal tshul mdzad //
NK090(u)006:151: rgyal mchog bde chen sa la rab bzhugs te //
NK090(u)006:152: smra ba'i las mchog rdo rje lce 'bar bas //
NK090(u)006:153: sgra dbyangs rgyal ba rnams kyis bdag byin rlobs //
NK090(u)006:154: gsang sngags rgyal po chos kyi me long 'di //
NK090(u)006:155: rgyal mchog chos kyi rgyal po nyid kyi mthus //
NK090(u)006:156: 'dus pa'i tshogs la rgya cher brjod par 'os //
NK090(u)006:157: a hoh zhes gsol ba btab /
NK090(u)006:159: badz+ra karma sat+wa tsakra ha ha hoh zhes brjod la sems dpa' rdo rje'i nga rgyal bya /
NK090(u)006:160: de nas slob dpon gyis bdud tshar gcod kyi sngags bzlas /
NK090(u)006:161: rtsa ba'i bla ma'i gsol 'debs dang chos bskul sngon du 'gro bas sems bskyed gsal gdab /
NK090(u)006:162: sngags kyi khyad par gyi kun slong rnams kyang bshad la /
NK090(u)006:163: spyi mdo'i che ba brjod pa ci rigs sngon du
NK090(u)006:164: btang nas chos rje dam pa'i mdo yi khog dbub
NK090(u)006:166: dka' 'grel rnams kyi bshad lung sngon du btang /
NK090(u)006:167: mdo dngos la chos rje dam pa'i bsdus don dang
NK090(u)006:168: skabs su sbyar mdo gzhung rtsa ba dal bus 'grel
NK090(u)006:169: pa dang sbrags te btang ba'am /
NK090(u)006:170: le'u re re bton rjes dka' 'grel mun pa'i go
NK090(u)006:171: cha nyid tshig ma chad par brda' 'phrod par bklag
NK090(u)006:172: / 'chad shes na bar skabs su spyi don du
NK090(u)006:173: chos rje dam pa'i mchan nyid kyis rtsa ba la
NK090(u)006:174: 'bru mnan byas te bshad na'ang shin tu legs par
NK090(u)006:175: / 'gyur ro // chos thun grol ba na dge bsngo dang /
NK090(u)006:176: tshogs man chad sgrub thabs dkyus ltar ro //
NK090(u)006:177: nyin rjes ma rnams la sgrub thabs rgyas pa ma grub na /
NK090(u)006:178: 'jigs med gling pas mdzad pa'i 'dus mdo'i rgyun khyer ram /
NK090(u)006:179: gter chen mchog gling gi lung rdo rje bkod pa'i
NK090(u)006:180: phyi dkyil dang lus dkyil gang rung zhig btang na'ang
NK090(u)006:182: legs ldan gtor chog ma chags par bya /
NK090(u)006:184: gzhung dngos rdzogs par grub rjes /
NK090(u)006:185: 'grel chen gyi dbu gsham lung bklag /bla ma dpal
NK090(u)006:186: chen po dang gsang ba'i mdo chen po nyid la
NK090(u)006:187: ched du brjod cing bstod pa'i glu blang ba 'di'i
NK090(u)006:188: rjes zlos / e ma ho skyes chen gsang ba'i bdag /rtsal chen smra ba seng ge'i sgra //
NK090(u)006:189: de bzhin gshegs la kun gyi thugs //
NK090(u)006:190: sangs rgyas kun sngon ye nas byung //
NK090(u)006:191: khyod ni sangs rgyas kun gyi mes //
NK090(u)006:192: che mchog rje btsan dam pa'i sku //
NK090(u)006:193: bde gshegs kun gyi bshes gnyen mchog /sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK090(u)006:194: kun gyi 'byung gnas me long gsal //
NK090(u)006:195: phyogs kun gsal 'grel nges pa'i mdo //
NK090(u)006:196: theg chen rmad grags ngo mtshar che //
NK090(u)006:197: gsang chen byung tshul ngo mtshar che //
NK090(u)006:198: a hoh zhes nges pa dam par mngon par bstod /
NK090(u)006:199: de ltar sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i
NK090(u)006:200: mdo chen po'i bshad bka' zab mo legs par thob
NK090(u)006:201: pa'i bka' drin gtang rag gi yon du man+dala phul
NK090(u)006:202: mdzod / man+dala tshom bu so bdun ma rgyas par phul dang /
NK090(u)006:203: 'di lta bu'i rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di nyid dbang
NK090(u)006:204: ma thob pa dang snod min la mi ster zhing
NK090(u)006:205: snod ldan nges pa can la sbyin pa dang /
NK090(u)006:206: bshad sgrub kyi phrin las nam mkha' dang mnyam par
NK090(u)006:207: bgyi ba'i sgo nas don gnyis rlabs po che sgrub
NK090(u)006:210: deng nas brtsams te sogs brjod /
NK090(u)006:211: spyi bsngo'i mtshams sbyor rgyas par spros nas bsngo smon gyis rgyas gdab /
NK090(u)006:212: rgyud chog gi tshul du sgrub thabs bka' ma ltar 'don tshogs la rol ba'i rjes /
NK090(u)006:213: spyi mdo dgongs 'dus sam rtsa rgyud kun 'dus rig
NK090(u)006:214: pa'i mdo lta bu slob ma du yod la dpe
NK090(u)006:215: bgos nas tshar gcig bton na shin tu legs /
NK090(u)006:217: bla ma sangs rgyas chos tshogs la //
NK090(u)006:218: byang chub bar du skyabs su mchi //
NK090(u)006:219: gzhan don rdzogs byang thob bya'i phyir //
NK090(u)006:220: zab mo'i rgyud sde bklag par bgyi //
NK090(u)006:222: bdag nyid gsang chog skur gsal zhing //
NK090(u)006:223: ngo bo nyid med gsang ba'i snying //
NK090(u)006:224: gsung gi byin rlabs rang snang ba //
NK090(u)006:225: rten 'byung sgra brnyan lta bu'i tshul //
NK090(u)006:226: dbyings las a byung a las ni //
NK090(u)006:227: yi ge yid bzhin sprin tshogs 'phros //
NK090(u)006:228: a ni rang bzhin yi ge ste //
NK090(u)006:229: rten dang bral bas rgyu rkyen med //
NK090(u)006:230: khong nas kun khyab nam mkha' 'dra //
NK090(u)006:231: chos nyid skye med zab mo yis //
NK090(u)006:232: chos kun khyab gnas zin pa ltar //
NK090(u)006:233: khyab gnas a yi rang bzhin gyis //
NK090(u)006:234: yi ge kun khyab kun zin te //
NK090(u)006:235: ming dang tshig tshogs sna tshogs bsgyur //
NK090(u)006:236: skyes bu thugs kyi dpal be'u nas //
NK090(u)006:237: thams cad 'byung ba kun gyi gzhi //
NK090(u)006:238: mgur gyi gsang ba'i dbyings su shar //
NK090(u)006:239: cho 'phrul yi ge lngar snang ba //
NK090(u)006:240: mgur gyi sgra byung mgur las grags //
NK090(u)006:241: a ka kha ga g+ha nga /
NK090(u)006:243: ljags kyi dbang po zla gam 'phros //
NK090(u)006:244: cho 'phrul yi ge lngar snang ba //
NK090(u)006:245: ljags kyi sgra byung ljags las grags //
NK090(u)006:247: a yi 'od zer rtse mo las //
NK090(u)006:248: ljags kyi zla gam rtse mo 'phros //
NK090(u)006:249: cho 'phrul lnga gnyis yi ger snang //
NK090(u)006:250: rtse mor sgra byung thor tor grags //
NK090(u)006:253: de bzhin de las de byung bas //
NK090(u)006:255: de bzhin yig 'bru lngar snang bas //
NK090(u)006:256: zhal gyi sgor byung zhal las grags //
NK090(u)006:258: yig 'bru kun gyi mchog de nyid //
NK090(u)006:259: gsang gi rgyun lam der byung ba //
NK090(u)006:260: yul la rigs pa'i 'bru shar ba //
NK090(u)006:261: cho 'phrul yi ge sna tshogs snang //
NK090(u)006:270: ri ri li li a hoh zhes brjod la rgyud bklag pa'i rjes /
NK090(u)006:274: e ma hoh nyes bcom legs ldan mtshan bzhi mtha' las 'das //
NK090(u)006:275: dpag med byams snyoms don gyis bdag gzhan dpal //
NK090(u)006:276: don dam gsang sbas nam mkha'i dkyil du 'khyil //
NK090(u)006:277: rdo rje che mchog dbang phyug kun gyi bdag /
NK090(u)006:278: 'dzin pa mi rtog sha rus khrag la rol //
NK090(u)006:279: thugs kyi gdung thag 'khor ba'i mtha' la rje //
NK090(u)006:280: yul med ma skyes mtshan ma'i g.yul las rgyal //
NK090(u)006:281: bde mchog rgyal po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK090(u)006:282: shes rab chen po nam mkha' nyi mar gsal //
NK090(u)006:283: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer dbyings su 'char //
NK090(u)006:284: dpal brtul myur ba'i shugs kyis 'gro drug sgrol //
NK090(u)006:285: rtog 'dzoms ye shes rdo rje cho 'phrul 'phro //
NK090(u)006:286: dam pa'i don gsung gnyis med ston pa'i sku //
NK090(u)006:287: smra ba'i seng ge mchog la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK090(u)006:288: rin chen gter ldan 'dod rgu kun skong zhing //
NK090(u)006:289: lung dang rigs pa gtan tshigs kun gyi mdzod //
NK090(u)006:290: brda can yan lag len pa'i me long gsal //
NK090(u)006:291: rdo rje kun 'dus 'jigs byed rgyal po'i rgyud //
NK090(u)006:292: chos kyi me long 'di la bdag cag 'dud //
NK090(u)006:297: brtan ma sogs sgrub thabs dkyus ltar nas bsngo smon
NK090(u)006:298: bkra shis rgyas par brjod pas dge legs su bya'o
NK090(u)006:299: // de ltar 'chad pa'i nyin grangs kyang zhag bco
NK090(u)006:300: lnga'am bdun las mi nyung bar nges par dgos so
NK090(u)006:301: // // 'di dge'i bsod nams grub pa gang yod des //
NK090(u)006:302: grong khyer gsum du gnas rnams dbugs 'byin zhing //
NK090(u)006:303: ye shes bla ma'i sa mchog thob nas kyang //
NK090(u)006:304: don gnyis lhun grub 'bad med 'byung bar shog //
NK090(u)006:305: ces pa'i rgyud kyi 'chad thabs nyung ngu 'di kahthoga
NK090(u)006:306: rdo rje gdan gyi chos grwa chen por rgyud 'di'i
NK090(u)006:307: bshad lung 'bogs pa'i skabs mkhas pa'i dbang phyug mkhan
NK090(u)006:308: legs 'byor dang nus ldan zung gis gsung bskul ngor
NK090(u)006:309: 'jam dbyangs blo gros rgya mtshos smras pa yi ge
NK090(u)006:310: pa ni 'gyur med bkra shis kyis bgyis pa 'dis
NK090(u)006:311: kyang gsang ba mchog gi bstan pa nyin mo ltar
